---
name: {{name}}
description: {{description}}
params:
  {{param_name}}: {{param_description}}
---

Workflow:

{{#each agents}}
orchestration:{{this.name}}:"{{this.task}}"{{#unless @last}} ->{{/unless}}
{{/each}}

{{!--
USAGE:

Variables:
- {{name}} - имя пайплайна в kebab-case
- {{description}} - описание пайплайна
- {{param_name}} - имя параметра
- {{param_description}} - описание параметра
- {{agents}} - массив агентов

Each agent:
- {{name}} - имя агента
- {{task}} - описание задачи

OPERATORS:
- -> sequential
- || parallel (wrap in [])
- ~> conditional
- @review:"question" checkpoint

EXAMPLES:

Sequential:
orchestration:analyzer:"Analyze {{topic}}" ->
orchestration:processor:"Process results" ->
orchestration:reporter:"Generate report"

Parallel:
[orchestration:web-search:"Search web" || orchestration:doc-search:"Search docs"] ->
orchestration:aggregator:"Merge results"

With review:
orchestration:analyzer:"Analyze" ->
@review:"Approve analysis?" ->
orchestration:processor:"Process"

Conditional:
orchestration:validator:"Check {{target}}" ->
(if valid)~> orchestration:processor:"Process" ~>
(else)~> orchestration:error-handler:"Handle errors"
--}}
